    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.43333333333333335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます\n{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚\n{user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、早いね\nまだ約束の30分前だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning. You’re early.\nIt’s 30 minutes before the appointed time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……ひょっとして、早過ぎましたか？\nつい、いつものクセで……すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Am I too early?\nI’m sorry… It’s a habit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は話だけだし、あまり身構えないで大丈夫だよ\nここは君の事務所なんだから、リラックスしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No need to be tense. We’re just here to chat.\nThis is your agency’s office now. Take it easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でもバンプロの時、事務所では\nいつも緊張感を持つようにしていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things were always rather tense\nwhen I was at Van Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロでは、打ち合わせでもそんな空気なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was it that way in Van Productions’ briefings too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロというか、父――朝倉社長の前では……\nどうしても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess it’s not so much Van Productions as when I’m in front of dad—\nI mean‚ President Asakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺の手本は三枝さんだからな……\n星見プロは三枝さんに似て、もっとおおらかな社風だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Well‚ I learned everything under Saegusa-san…\nThe culture of Hoshimi Productions is more casual‚ like Saegusa-san himself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです。バンプロとまるで雰囲気が違うので\n最初の頃は私達、戸惑っていたんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can tell. It feels very different from Van Productions.\nIt was a little perplexing at first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}